<section class="guaranteed-rent" id="rentabilidade-garantida">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="header-badge">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
          <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"/>
        </svg>
        Rentabilidade Garantida
      </div>
      <h2>Durma Descansado. O Seu Rendimento Está Garantido.</h2>
      <p>Sem preocupações com vacância, sem surpresas desagradáveis. Apenas um valor fixo na sua conta todos os meses, como um relógio.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero Visual -->
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="visual-card main-card">
        <div class="card-header">
          <span class="card-label">O Seu Rendimento Mensal</span>
          <div class="guaranteed-badge">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="16" height="16">
              <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4z"/>
            </svg>
            100% Garantido
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="amount-display">
          <span class="currency">€</span>
          <span class="amount">1.200</span>
          <span class="period">/mês</span>
        </div>
        <div class="payment-info">
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Independente da ocupação</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Pagamento pontual garantido</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-item">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
              <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Contratos de 3-5 anos</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="visual-stats">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon green">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M16 6l2.29 2.29-4.88 4.88-4-4L2 16.59 3.41 18l6-6 4 4 6.3-6.29L22 12V6z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-content">
            <span class="stat-value">100%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Taxa de Ocupação Garantida</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon blue">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M11.8 10.9c-2.27-.59-3-1.2-3-2.15 0-1.09 1.01-1.85 2.7-1.85 1.78 0 2.44.85 2.5 2.1h2.21c-.07-1.72-1.12-3.3-3.21-3.81V3h-3v2.16c-1.94.42-3.5 1.68-3.5 3.61 0 2.31 1.91 3.46 4.7 4.13 2.5.6 3 1.48 3 2.41 0 .69-.49 1.79-2.7 1.79-2.06 0-2.87-.92-2.98-2.1h-2.2c.12 2.19 1.76 3.42 3.68 3.83V21h3v-2.15c1.95-.37 3.5-1.5 3.5-3.55 0-2.84-2.43-3.81-4.7-4.4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-content">
            <span class="stat-value">0€</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Custos com Manutenção</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-icon orange">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="24" height="24">
              <path d="M19 3h-1V1h-2v2H8V1H6v2H5c-1.11 0-1.99.9-1.99 2L3 19c0 1.1.89 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 16H5V8h14v11zM7 10h5v5H7z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-content">
            <span class="stat-value">12 meses</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Rendimento Anual Previsível</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How it Works -->
    <div class="how-it-works">
      <h3>Como Funciona o Modelo de Rentabilidade Garantida?</h3>
      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Avaliação Profissional</h4>
            <p>Visitamos o seu imóvel e fazemos uma análise detalhada do potencial de mercado, localização e características únicas.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Proposta Transparente</h4>
            <p>Apresentamos uma proposta clara com o valor de renda mensal garantida e duração do contrato (normalmente 3-5 anos).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Contrato de Arrendamento</h4>
            <p>Assinamos um contrato de arrendamento onde nos comprometemos a pagar o valor fixo mensal, independentemente da ocupação.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M12 4l-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H4v2h12.17l-5.58 5.59L12 20l8-8z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step-card">
          <div class="step-number">4</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h4>Receba Mensalmente</h4>
            <p>Todos os meses, no mesmo dia, recebe o valor acordado na sua conta. Simples, previsível, garantido.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Comparison -->
    <div class="comparison-section">
      <h3>Rentabilidade Garantida vs Risco de Mercado</h3>
      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <div class="comparison-card left">
          <div class="comparison-header traditional">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28">
              <path d="M1 21h22L12 2 1 21zm12-3h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2v-4h2v4z"/>
            </svg>
            <h4>Modelo Tradicional</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="comparison-list negative">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
              </svg>
              Rendimento varia mensalmente
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
              </svg>
              Períodos de vacância sem receita
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
              </svg>
              Despesas surpresa de manutenção
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
              </svg>
              Impossível planear financeiramente
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M19 6.41L17.59 5 12 10.59 6.41 5 5 6.41 10.59 12 5 17.59 6.41 19 12 13.41 17.59 19 19 17.59 13.41 12z"/>
              </svg>
              Preocupação constante com ocupação
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-divider">
          <span>VS</span>
        </div>

        <div class="comparison-card right">
          <div class="comparison-header guaranteed">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="28" height="28">
              <path d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4z"/>
            </svg>
            <h4>Rentabilidade Garantida</h4>
          </div>
          <ul class="comparison-list positive">
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
              </svg>
              Valor fixo todos os meses
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
              </svg>
              100% de ocupação garantida
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
              </svg>
              Todas as despesas por nossa conta
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
              </svg>
              Previsibilidade financeira total
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="20" height="20">
                <path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41L9 16.17z"/>
              </svg>
              Zero preocupações ou stress
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Ideal For -->
    <div class="ideal-for">
      <h3>Este Modelo é Ideal Para Quem...</h3>
      <div class="ideal-grid">
        <div class="ideal-card">
          <div class="ideal-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M16.5 3c-1.74 0-3.41.81-4.5 2.09C10.91 3.81 9.24 3 7.5 3 4.42 3 2 5.42 2 8.5c0 3.78 3.4 6.86 8.55 11.54L12 21.35l1.45-1.32C18.6 15.36 22 12.28 22 8.5 22 5.42 19.58 3 16.5 3zm-4.4 15.55l-.1.1-.1-.1C7.14 14.24 4 11.39 4 8.5 4 6.5 5.5 5 7.5 5c1.54 0 3.04.99 3.57 2.36h1.87C13.46 5.99 14.96 5 16.5 5c2 0 3.5 1.5 3.5 3.5 0 2.89-3.14 5.74-7.9 10.05z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Valoriza Tranquilidade</h4>
          <p>Não quer preocupações com gestão, ocupação ou manutenção do imóvel</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ideal-card">
          <div class="ideal-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M19 3H5c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V5c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zM9 17H7v-7h2v7zm4 0h-2V7h2v10zm4 0h-2v-4h2v4z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Precisa de Previsibilidade</h4>
          <p>Quer saber exatamente quanto vai receber para planear o seu orçamento familiar</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ideal-card">
          <div class="ideal-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L19 8l-9 9z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Quer Segurança Garantida</h4>
          <p>Prefere um rendimento estável a arriscar ter períodos sem receita</p>
        </div>

        <div class="ideal-card">
          <div class="ideal-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="32" height="32">
              <path d="M11.99 2C6.47 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.47 10 9.99 10C17.52 22 22 17.52 22 12S17.52 2 11.99 2zM12 20c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm.5-13H11v6l5.25 3.15.75-1.23-4.5-2.67z"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h4>Não Tem Tempo</h4>
          <p>Vive longe, viaja frequentemente ou simplesmente não tem disponibilidade para gerir</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA Final -->
    <div class="final-cta">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>Interessado em Rentabilidade Garantida?</h3>
        <p>Solicite uma avaliação gratuita do seu imóvel e descubra quanto pode receber mensalmente com total segurança.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contacto" class="btn-primary-large">
            Solicitar Avaliação Gratuita
          </a>
          <a href="/como-funciona" class="btn-secondary-outline">
            Saber Mais
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .guaranteed-rent {
    padding: 100px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, white 0%, var(--blue-light) 50%, white 100%);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Header */
  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 80px;
  }

  .header-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 30px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(12, 68, 99, 0.2);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  /* Hero Visual */
  .hero-visual {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  .main-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 48px;
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(12, 68, 99, 0.3);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .main-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -50%;
    right: -50%;
    width: 200%;
    height: 200%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
    50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  .card-header {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .guaranteed-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 6px 16px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .amount-display {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .currency {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .amount {
    font-size: 5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .period {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-left: 12px;
  }

  .payment-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .info-item svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: 4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  /* Visual Stats */
  .visual-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 24px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .stat-card:hover {
    transform: translateX(8px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .stat-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .stat-icon.green { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%); color: white; }
  .stat-icon.blue { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%); color: white; }
  .stat-icon.orange { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); color: white; }

  .stat-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  /* How it Works */
  .how-it-works {
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  .how-it-works h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .step-card {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .step-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--secondary);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-8px);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 auto 20px;
  }

  .step-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .step-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: -28px;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    color: var(--secondary);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .step-card:last-child .step-arrow {
    display: none;
  }

  /* Comparison */
  .comparison-section {
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  .comparison-section h3 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .comparison-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .comparison-card {
    background: white;
